; How to build a package (without modifying source):
: dpkg-buildpackage --force-sign -B -sa -m<email>
: e.g.: dpkg-buildpackage --force-sign -sa -mHelge\ Deller\ \<deller@gmx.de\> -kB51E3864 -j5

